/* Early life and education */Page stated Marley attended Porlock School, then Walworth school for his GCSE (written as if it were a single qualification). It then goes on to say he graduated with distinction at Harris Academy Peckham. However, Walworth School is a special needs primary school in County Durham, meaning they wouldn’t issue GCSEs. Ark Academy Walworth might have been the intended institution, but he would have received his GCSEs and mentioned business studies qualification from...
